'''Elijah Ari''' (born 6 November 1987), sometimes also known as '''Elijah Aryee''', is a [[Ghana]]ian-[[Kyrgyzstan|Kyrgyz]] international footballer who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Bowsher Club]] in [[Oman]]. Born in Ghana, he moved to [[Central Asia]] in 2007, and played three seasons in [[Kyrgyzstan]] for [[FC Dordoi Bishkek|Dordoi Bishkek]].<ref name="profile">{{cite web|title=Elijah Ari, footballdatabase.eu profile |url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.elijah.ari.203897.en.html |accessdate=4 May 2014}}</ref>

==Club career==
The Ghanaian born Ari started his career in [[FC Dordoi Bishkek|Dordoi Bishkek]] where he played three seasons and acquired [[Kyrgyzstan]]i citizenship. He then spent one season with [[Vakhsh Qughonteppa]] in neighboring [[Tajikistan]]. He now plays for [[Bowsher Club]], in Oman.<ref name="profile"/><ref name="NFT" />

==International career==
Ari has eight national appearances for [[Kyrgyzstan national football team|Kyrgyzstan]] to his name.<ref name="profile"/>

